flowchart TD
    A[User opens Create and Join] --> B[Enter room ID and password if private]
    B --> C[Tap Join]
    C --> D[CreateJoinGameWidget._joinRoom]
    D --> E[checkCoinsRequirement]
    E --> F[ensureWebSocketReady]
    F --> G{Already in this room}
    G -->|Yes| H[setCurrentGameSync]
    H --> I[Navigate to game-play]
    G -->|No| J[DutchGameHelpers.joinRoom]
    J --> K[clearAllGameStateBeforeNewGame]
    K --> L[Emit join_room]
    L --> M[Backend join room]
    M --> N[websocket_join_room success]
    N --> O[State currentGameId currentRoomId isInRoom]
    O --> P[Wait 300ms]
    P --> Q{games contains roomId}
    Q -->|Yes| H
    Q -->|No| R[Wait 400ms retry]
    R --> Q
    I --> S[Joiner sees game no Start button]
